{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1655/comments/7262090.json"}, "code": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/diff/osrf/gazebo:273ecd3a64ad..dd78a778ce02?path=cmake%2FSearchForStuff.cmake"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1655/_/diff#comment-7262090"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1655, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1655.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1655"}}, "title": "Mentor 2 MOOC related bug fixes and enhancements"}, "content": {"raw": "I think this won't work on Windows but you could do something like:\n\n\n```\n#!c++\n# Find uuid\n#  - In UNIX we use uuid library.\n#  - In Windows the native RPC call, no dependency needed.\nif (UNIX)\n  pkg_check_modules(uuid uuid)\n  if (uuid_FOUND)\n    message (STATUS \"Looking for uuid - found\")\n    set (HAVE_UUID TRUE)\n  else ()\n    set (HAVE_UUID FALSE)\n    BUILD_WARNING (\"uuid-dev library not found - Gazebo will not have uuid support.\")\n  endif ()\nelse()\n  message (STATUS \"Using Windows RPC UuidCreate function\")\n  set (HAVE_UUID TRUE)\nendif()\n```", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I think this won't work on Windows but you could do something like:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite language-c++\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"cp\"># Find uuid</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#  - In UNIX we use uuid library.</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#  - In Windows the native RPC call, no dependency needed.</span>\n<span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">UNIX</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">pkg_check_modules</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">uuid</span> <span class=\"n\">uuid</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">uuid_FOUND</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">message</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">STATUS</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Looking for uuid - found&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">HAVE_UUID</span> <span class=\"n\">TRUE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">else</span> <span class=\"p\">()</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">HAVE_UUID</span> <span class=\"n\">FALSE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">BUILD_WARNING</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;uuid-dev library not found - Gazebo will not have uuid support.&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">endif</span> <span class=\"p\">()</span>\n<span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">message</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">STATUS</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Using Windows RPC UuidCreate function&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">set</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">HAVE_UUID</span> <span class=\"n\">TRUE</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">endif</span><span class=\"p\">()</span>\n</pre></div>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-06-03T00:54:39.169698+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Carlos Ag\u00fcero", "uuid": "{da8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bda8a8e89-4bb0-421b-bd0e-dbbed3d4ed6a%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/692bf15758111acaddae4da15a47f9e5d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCA-0.png"}}, "nickname": "caguero", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:4ded1ddf-947e-4154-bbd1-3dba24f1bdbd"}, "inline": {"to": 562, "from": null, "outdated": true, "path": "cmake/SearchForStuff.cmake"}, "updated_on": "2015-06-03T00:54:39.181617+